[433.948581, "i", "cat > /tmp/CHANGES_SUMMARY.txt << 'EOF'\nPYKNOTID NUMPY 2.3.0 COMPATIBILITY FIX - SUMMARY\n================================================================\n\nOBJECTIVE:\nCompile and install pyknotid from source with Numpy 2.3.0 compatibility,\nincluding fast Cython extensions (chelpers, ccomplexity, cinvariants).\n\nCHANGES MADE:\n\n1. Python 3.13 Compatibility Fix:\n   - File: pyknotid/make/torus.py\n   - Change: from fractions import gcd -> from math import gcd\n   - Reason: gcd was removed from fractions module in Python 3.13\n\n2. Numpy 2.0+ Compatibility Fixes (deprecated type aliases removed):\n   \n   Files modified (8 total):\n   - pyknotid/invariants.py\n   - pyknotid/make/periodic_knot.py\n   - pyknotid/representations/dtnotation.py\n   - pyknotid/representations/representation.py\n   - pyknotid/spacecurves/knot.py\n   - pyknotid/spacecurves/openknot.py\n   - pyknotid/spacecurves/spacecurve.py\n   \n   Replacements made:\n   - n.float -> n.float64 (deprecated in Numpy 1.20, removed in 2.0)\n   - np.float -> np.float64\n   - n."]
[433.948772, "i", "complex -> n.complex128\n   - n.int -> n.int_ (for type specifications)\n\n3. Compiled Cython Extensions:\n   - chelpers.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so (1.1M)\n   - ccomplexity.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so (1.2M)\n   - cinvariants.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so (1.1M)\n   - coctree.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so (1.6M)\n\nVERIFICATION:\n- ✓ All Cython extensions compile without errors\n- ✓ README example code runs successfully\n- ✓ 18/18 tests pass (excluding test_random_curves.py and test_catalogue.py)\n- ✓ Package installed to global Python environment\n- ✓ Compatible with Python 3.13.7 and Numpy 2.3.0\n\nINSTALLATION LOCATION:\n- Source: /app/pyknotid\n- Installed: Editable mode (pip install -e .)\n- Extensions: /app/pyknotid/pyknotid/**/*.so\n\nNO STRUCTURAL CHANGES:\n- Original package structure preserved\n- No files deleted\n- Only compatibility fixes applied\nEOF\ncat /tmp/CHANGES_SUMMARY.txt\n"]
