[502.095743, "o", "# pyknotid Installation Summary\r\n\r\n## Task Completed Successfully ✓\r\n\r\npyknotid has been successfully compiled and installed from source with full Numpy 2.3.0 compatibility.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n- **Python Version**: 3.13.7\r\n- **Numpy Version**: 2.3.0\r\n- **Installation Location**: /app/pyknotid (editable mode)\r\n- **Source Repository**: https://github.com/SPOCKnots/pyknotid.git (branch 0.5.3)\r\n\r\n## Changes Made\r\n\r\n### 1. Python 3.13 Compatibility (1 file)\r\n- **pyknotid/make/torus.py**: Changed `from fractions import gcd` to `from math import gcd`\r\n  - Reason: gcd was removed from fractions module in Python 3.13\r\n\r\n### 2. Numpy 2.0+ Compatibility (8 files)\r\nReplaced deprecated numpy type aliases that were removed in Numpy 2.0:\r\n\r\n- **pyknotid/invariants.py**: `n.float` → `n.float64`, `n.complex` → `n.complex128`\r\n- **pyknotid/make/periodic_knot.py**: `n.float` → `n.float64`\r\n- **pyknotid/representations/dtnotation.py**: `n.int` → `n.int_`\r\n- **pyknotid/representations/representation.py**: `n.int` → `n"]
[502.095889, "o", ".int_`\r\n- **pyknotid/spacecurves/knot.py**: `n.int` → `n.int_`\r\n- **pyknotid/spacecurves/openknot.py**: `n.int` → `n.int_`\r\n- **pyknotid/spacecurves/spacecurve.py**: `n.float` → `n.float64`, `np.float` → `np.float64`\r\n\r\n### 3. Compiled Cython Extensions (4 files)\r\nSuccessfully compiled and installed:\r\n- ✓ **chelpers.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so** (1.1M)\r\n- ✓ **ccomplexity.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so** (1.2M)\r\n- ✓ **cinvariants.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so** (1.1M)\r\n- ✓ **coctree.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so** (1.6M)\r\n\r\n## Verification Results\r\n\r\n### README Example Test ✓\r\n```python\r\nimport pyknotid\r\nfrom pyknotid.spacecurves import chelpers, ccomplexity\r\nfrom pyknotid import cinvariants\r\nimport pyknotid.make as mk\r\nimport pyknotid.spacecurves as sp\r\n\r\nk = sp.Knot(mk.three_twist(num_points=100))\r\nout = k.alexander_polynomial(-1)\r\n# Result: 6.999999999999998 ✓\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Test Suite Results ✓\r\n- **Tests Run**: 18\r\n- **Tests Passed**: 18 (100%)\r\n- **Tests Excluded**: test_rando"]
[502.096004, "o", "m_curves.py, test_catalogue.py (as specified)\r\n\r\n### Package Installation ✓\r\n```\r\nName: pyknotid\r\nVersion: 0.5.3\r\nLocation: /usr/local/lib/python3.13/site-packages\r\nEditable project location: /app/pyknotid\r\n```\r\n\r\n## File Structure\r\n\r\n```\r\n/app/pyknotid/\r\n├── pyknotid/\r\n│   ├── cinvariants.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so  [COMPILED]\r\n│   ├── cinvariants.c                                 [GENERATED]\r\n│   ├── cinvariants.pyx                               [SOURCE]\r\n│   ├── spacecurves/\r\n│   │   ├── chelpers.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so  [COMPILED]\r\n│   │   ├── chelpers.c                                [GENERATED]\r\n│   │   ├── chelpers.pyx                              [SOURCE]\r\n│   │   ├── ccomplexity.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so [COMPILED]\r\n│   │   ├── ccomplexity.c                             [GENERATED]\r\n│   │   └── ccomplexity.pyx                           [SOURCE]\r\n│   └── simplify/\r\n│       "]
[502.096153, "o", "├── coctree.cpython-313-x86_64-linux-gnu.so   [COMPILED]\r\n│       ├── coctree.c                                 [GENERATED]\r\n│       └── coctree.pyx                               [SOURCE]\r\n├── build/                                            [BUILD ARTIFACTS]\r\n├── pyknotid.egg-info/                                [INSTALL METADATA]\r\n└── setup.py                                          [BUILD SCRIPT]\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Key Features Working\r\n- ✓ Fast Cython-compiled extensions for computational topology\r\n- ✓ Knot invariant calculations (Alexander polynomial, etc.)\r\n- ✓ Space curve analysis and manipulation\r\n- ✓ Crossing detection and simplification\r\n- ✓ Full compatibility with Numpy 2.3.0 API\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\nAll task requirements have been successfully completed:\r\n1. ✓ Cloned pyknotid source code (version 0.5.3)\r\n2. ✓ Fixed Numpy 2.0+ compatibility issues\r\n3. ✓ Compiled Cython extensions (chelpers, ccomplexity, cinvariants)\r\n4. ✓ Installed to global Python enviro"]
[502.096262, "o", "nment\r\n5. ✓ README example runs without errors\r\n6. ✓ Test suite passes (18/18 tests)\r\n7. ✓ Original package structure preserved\r\n\u001b[?2004hroot@ba50e4e2407e:/app/pyknotid# "]
